	[em 
		"Dead Zone
	]em
	" is an adventure game by Sunsoft for the Famicom Disk System released in 1986. Kirk McRae and his beloved Mary were set on getting married, only for it to be delayed due to Mary's new job at Linoex. She gave Kirk a robot gift named Carry prior to her departure. Later, Kirk receives a message from Mary to invite him to celebrate the Lionex project a month early... however, when he arrives, the colony was empty and he gets knocked out. It is up to him to figure what happened.
